.br
Ctx = [#\&'IOP_ServiceContext\&'{}]
.br
Op = atom()
.br
Args = [Argument] - defined in the IDL-specification
.br
Reply = {NewArgs, NewExtra}
.br
.RE
.RE
.RS
.LP
Before a request is sent to the server side ORB, \fIout_request\fR\& is invoked\&.
.RE
.LP
